        {
            "title": "油價急挫逾9% 霍爾木茲海峽重開成關鍵",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">國際油價週四（17日）急挫，英美兩大期油均錄得逾9%跌幅。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"油價\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/Oil.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"油價\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/Oil.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">油價</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">紐約期油跌幅更深，低見80.56美元，跌幅近15%，收市報83.85美元，急挫10.84美元，跌幅達11.4%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">倫敦布蘭特期油一度低見每桶86.09美元，跌幅超過13%，最終收報每桶90.38美元，大跌9.01美元，跌幅近9.1%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">伊朗表示，在黎巴嫩與以色列停火期間，將對所有商船開放霍爾木茲海峽，緩解了供應中斷的憂慮。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15887932-%e6%b2%b9%e5%83%b9%e6%80%a5%e6%8c%ab%e9%80%be9-%e9%9c%8d%e7%88%be%e6%9c%a8%e8%8c%b2%e6%b5%b7%e5%b3%bd%e9%87%8d%e9%96%8b%e6%88%90%e9%97%9c%e9%8d%b5",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/8a6d6fb35c89d9b0db4c4846f290c2c3_Iran_US_Oil_Prices_19824_FB.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-18 11:04:29",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美股三大指數連升三周 納指標指再創新高",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美股三大指數周五全線造好，道瓊斯工業平均指數升近兩個高位，標準普爾500指數首破7100點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20200305_FI_US-STOCK_FB-1-1-1-1-2-1-1-2-1-1-1-1-1_source-ap_-4.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20200305_FI_US-STOCK_FB-1-1-1-1-2-1-1-2-1-1-1-1-1_source-ap_-4.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">伊朗宣布在以色列與黎巴嫩停火協議期間，霍爾木茲海峽將全面向商船開放，美國總統特朗普亦稱伊朗已清除所有水雷。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20200305_FI_US-STOCK_FB-1-1-1-1-2-1-1-2-1-1-1-1-1_source-ap_-4.png.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20200305_FI_US-STOCK_FB-1-1-1-1-2-1-1-2-1-1-1-1-1_source-ap_-4.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/b462b82f1e202f28a75ab1a8070c00b7_Apple_5_th_Anniversary_22569.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/644x392/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/b462b82f1e202f28a75ab1a8070c00b7_Apple_5_th_Anniversary_22569.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/bplib_20250224-182216_20250224_Netflix_source-web-3.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"資料圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/bplib_20250224-182216_20250224_Netflix_source-web-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">資料圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"高盛 Goldman Sachs 。 Shutterstock圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250417_FI_source_licensed_Goldman_shutterstock.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"高盛 Goldman Sachs 。 Shutterstock圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250417_FI_source_licensed_Goldman_shutterstock.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">高盛 Goldman Sachs 。 Shutterstock圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20200305_FI_US-STOCK_FB-1-1-1-1-2-1-1-2-1-1-1-1-1_source-ap_-4.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/644x392/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/b462b82f1e202f28a75ab1a8070c00b7_Apple_5_th_Anniversary_22569.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"資料圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/bplib_20250224-182216_20250224_Netflix_source-web-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">資料圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"高盛 Goldman Sachs 。 Shutterstock圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250417_FI_source_licensed_Goldman_shutterstock.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">高盛 Goldman Sachs 。 Shutterstock圖片</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>納指連升13日創紀錄</strong></p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">道瓊斯工業平均指數收市報49447點，升868點或約1.8%，創下自2月下旬以來的收市高位。高開210點後，升幅擴大至最多1139點，高見49717點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">納斯達克指數收報24468點，升365點或1.5%，一度漲1.73%，破頂至24519點。連續13個交易日上漲，創下自1992年以來最長的連升紀錄。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">標準普爾500指數收報7126點，升84點或1.2%。曾揚升1.51%至7147點，連續3天刷新紀錄。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">納指與標普500指數均連續第三個交易日創下歷史新高。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/b462b82f1e202f28a75ab1a8070c00b7_Apple_5_th_Anniversary_22569.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/b462b82f1e202f28a75ab1a8070c00b7_Apple_5_th_Anniversary_22569.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>科技股普遍向好 金融股造好</strong></p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">大型科技股多數向上，蘋果（AAPL）升2.6%，特斯拉（TSLA）升3%。英偉達（NVDA）升1.68%、Alphabet（GOOGL）升1.68%，Meta（META）升1.73%。有報道指Meta計劃於下月20日啟動今年首輪大規模裁員，涉及約10%全球員工，即近8000人，公司並計劃在下半年進一步裁員。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Netflix次季業績指引遜色，加上宣布主席將退出董事局，股價逆市挫9.7%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/bplib_20250224-182216_20250224_Netflix_source-web-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"資料圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/bplib_20250224-182216_20250224_Netflix_source-web-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">資料圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">英特爾曾升2.7%至70.33美元，創2000年以來新高，今年累計一度飆約88%；不過，收市蒸發所有升幅，反覆持平。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">金融股表現強勁，高盛（GS）升2.88%，美國運通（AXP）升1.82%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">航空股全線炒上，聯合航空股價勁升7.1%，美國航空及達美航空分別漲4.2%及2.6%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"高盛 Goldman Sachs 。 Shutterstock圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250417_FI_source_licensed_Goldman_shutterstock.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"高盛 Goldman Sachs 。 Shutterstock圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250417_FI_source_licensed_Goldman_shutterstock.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">高盛 Goldman Sachs 。 Shutterstock圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>霍爾木茲海峽重開 油股急跌</strong></p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">伊朗宣佈重開關鍵的霍爾木茲海峽，市場亦憧憬美國與伊朗可能達成協議，導致國際油價急挫。能源股受壓，雪佛龍（CVX）跌逾2%，成為跌幅最大的道指成份股。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>全周累積升幅顯著</strong></p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">總結全星期表現，道指累升約3.2%，納指累升6.8%，標普500指數累升4.5%，三大指數均連續第三個星期錄得升幅。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15887893-%e7%be%8e%e8%82%a1%e4%b8%89%e5%a4%a7%e6%8c%87%e6%95%b8%e9%80%a3%e5%8d%87%e4%b8%89%e5%91%a8-%e7%b4%8d%e6%8c%87%e6%a8%99%e6%8c%87%e5%86%8d%e5%89%b5%e6%96%b0%e9%ab%98",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20200617_FI_US-STOCK_FB-2-1-1-2-1-1-1-2-1-1-1-2-1_source-ap_-2.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-18 10:54:37",
