        {
            "title": "歐股全線高收 德法股市升逾2% 德股一周升3.8%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">歐洲主要股市周五全線造好，收市升幅介乎近1%至逾2%，主要受惠伊朗宣佈重開霍爾木茲海峽的消息。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"歐股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250318_FI_source-ap_Britain_Financial_Markets-4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"歐股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250318_FI_source-ap_Britain_Financial_Markets-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">歐股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>德法股市升幅顯著</strong></p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">德國DAX指數收報24702點，急升547點，升幅近2.3%。法國CAC指數收報8425點，上升162點，升幅近2%。英國富時100指數則升77點或0.7%，收報10667點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">意大利富時MIB指數收報48869點，升1.75%或842點；西班牙IBEX 35指數收報18484點，升2.18%或395點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>三大指數連升數週</strong></p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">總結全星期表現，德股累升近3.8%，連續第三周上揚。法股及英股分別累升2%及0.6%，兩者均錄得連續第四周上升。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15887869-%e6%ad%90%e8%82%a1%e5%85%a8%e7%b7%9a%e9%ab%98%e6%94%b6-%e5%be%b7%e6%b3%95%e8%82%a1%e5%b8%82%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be2-%e5%be%b7%e8%82%a1%e4%b8%80%e5%91%a8%e5%8d%873-8",
